# FOG Git 忽略规则
# 目标：GitHub 只保存共享 Skill、安装检查工具、README/AGENT 和 workspace 00-09 固定目录结构。

# 本地真实配置、个人配置、码表和本机维护清单
config/fog_config.yaml
config/fog_config.yaml.bak
config/personal_config.yaml
config/personal_config.yaml.bak
config/database.yaml
config/码表/

# 不分享的 Skill
.workbuddy/skills/lx-hhgongbu/
.workbuddy/skills/lx-hhdataimport/
.workbuddy/skills/lx-lxdataimport/
.workbuddy/skills/lx-txwendang/

# WorkBuddy 本地记忆和运行态
.workbuddy/memory/
.workbuddy/scripts/
.workbuddy/skills/*/assets/config.yaml
.workbuddy/skills/*/assets/cache/
.workbuddy/skills/*/assets/*cache*.json
.workbuddy/skills/*/assets/entity_cache.json
.workbuddy/skills/*/assets/dailyreport_cache.json
.workbuddy/skills/*/.token_cache

# 构建产物、依赖目录、海报输出
.workbuddy/skills/*/.venv/
.workbuddy/skills/*/node_modules/
.workbuddy/skills/*/dist/
.workbuddy/skills/*/build/
.workbuddy/skills/lx-haibao/output/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.log
.DS_Store

# 文档：只跟踪模板分发需要的维护文档，业务草稿和二进制文档继续忽略
docs/*
!docs/
!docs/管理员维护说明.md
!docs/模板更新与配置策略.md

# 初始化、备份、压缩包和临时交付物
.lx-init-report.md
.fog-update-report.md
.fog_backup/
.template_exports/
zip/
*.zip
*.tmp
*.tmp.*

